creator: Produce Pro, Inc.
descriptionHtml: UNITED SALAD CO. is one of the largest produce distribution channels in the Pacific Northwest. Our expansive refrigerated warehouses receive fresh produce seven days a week from those as close to our local farmers and expanding to growers all over the world, once received every item is closely inspected to ensure it meets our SQF standards, the highest food safety certification in our industry. Our consistent standards for freshness and handling give our customers the best of both worlds, garden fresh taste and superior appearance. United Salad Co has a long history of delivering fresh quality produce throughout the Pacific Northwest for the past 75 years. We continue to strive to meet consumer demands by not only offering the highest quality conventional and organic produce to the marketplace, but also a full line of custom-cut fruits and vegetables as well as grocery, dairy, and dry goods. Fresh for your Success. Right for our Environment.
